{"tid":1779650,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"中國版 Switch 開賣確認是閹割版！連線只能中國主機互相面連","createTime":"2019-12-11T22:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T18:09:00.000Z","uid":22675,"like":153,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"bfe64c1085313fe78eabefc6898d3f9e091ca5c3","tid":1779650,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T22:51:42.000Z","msg":"騰訊與任天堂合作將 Switch 帶入中國推出特製版本，然而發表會中雖然沒有完整說明連線的相關限制，但是發售當天還是吸引到不少玩家購買。於是今日根據外媒 A9VG 的實測，發現目前中國版主機似乎還無法進行連線對戰，部分遊戲也只能透過面連對戰。<br />\n<br />\n以目前狀況來說，中國版 Switch 的 eShop 只能利用當地的微信 QR 碼進行登入，所以無法手動輸入其他國家的帳號，強制登入中國版商店。不過在遊戲上是可以正常遊玩海外版實體遊戲，並能透過網路直接更新至最新版，但現階段還無法進行網路連線對戰，只能透過有支援面連的遊戲來進行。<br />\n<br />\n其他方面：<br />\n中國帳號可以搜尋到海外帳號的好友，但無法添加，反之亦然<br />\n<br />\n中國 Switch 無法與海外版 Switch 轉移帳號資料<br />\n<br />\n中國 Switch 無法上傳截圖到網路上<br />\n<br />\n支援所有海外如健身環、Pro 手把等配件<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HphRwGVSQ3CejTRBJjXnEw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQ4MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/U3OKHkUIe6JH4hC5OL42Jg--~B/aD0xMDgwO3c9MTQ0MDtzbT0xO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-12/f485b170-1be3-11ea-af57-8c86ae0fae10\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FHphRwGVSQ3CejTRBJjXnEw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQ4MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FU3OKHkUIe6JH4hC5OL42Jg--~B%2FaD0xMDgwO3c9MTQ0MDtzbT0xO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-12%2Ff485b170-1be3-11ea-af57-8c86ae0fae10&h=31f96fa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然騰訊在先前發布會有說過，未來還是會推出任天堂的網路會員，畢竟目前中國版 Switch 陣容中尚未有可以連線的遊戲出現，所以並不知道未來在網路連線上是否能與海外玩家遊玩。以目前狀況，不少中國網友也酸說：「請用&rdquo;可以玩NS卡帶的騰訊遊戲機&rdquo;來稱呼他」、「基本上需要帳號或是連線操作的都無法進行」、「等大神改機吧」、「河蟹主機賣這價錢...」、「網路連線繼續觀望好了」"},{"pid":"47ea31b8f4ff7324f295e220114f5247e6fc98d8","tid":1779650,"uid":210165,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T22:53:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2af943b8bb8906c910db3f5dd62e96191e150126","tid":1779650,"uid":7206,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T22:56:12.000Z","msg":"中國特色=閹割=太監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1023aee654563fc6258e8d69df6f7c35699ec9c3","tid":1779650,"uid":335874,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T23:01:54.000Z","msg":"都好嘅<br />\n廢事啲支那玩家見到其他玩家改啲名<br />\n玻璃心又碎<br />\n到時老任跪仲麻煩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed86f4c83506d4dc018d6ca55907c3b37c18f49e","tid":1779650,"uid":34828,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T23:05:23.000Z","msg":"全世界福音"},{"pid":"16e3d2b3c877881bcaeaf897d3c19a8b5ca76c02","tid":1779650,"uid":40272,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T23:05:27.000Z","msg":"明日香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a9429b0adfab7392c84f5ebcbc73feb449aa63","tid":1779650,"uid":3508,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T23:08:42.000Z","msg":"希望以後所有野都可以咁做<br />\n鎖死曬呢14億人自己打自己<br />\n唔好俾佢地走到出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b1e638e524abe4d09a37a0cd56ac75a2a43948","tid":1779650,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T23:10:20.000Z","msg":"咩都鎖哂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBy the way, 借宣傳一下個APP<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 - 黎投票啦！📊📊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1758886\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1758886</a>"},{"pid":"f911bbd05b615379a15b11853b5a101aaca8a128","tid":1779650,"uid":90315,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T23:10:42.000Z","msg":"聽聞個eshop